\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Nov 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104aep1665702782656.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/aep1665702782656.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/aep1665702782656.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"aep1665702782656\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $fact\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"aep1665702782656___fact_262743\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Calculate the factorial of X (X!).\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"aep1665702782656__topic_d82832e1_d82833e1_d82834e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aep1665702782656__p_d82835e1_d82836e1_d82837e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fact</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aep1665702782656__topic_d54687e1_d54688e1_d54689e1_d54690e1_d54691e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d966743e75\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aep1665702782656__p_d82841e1_d82842e1_d82843e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>—positive integer constant, or a field (or indirect reference to a field), a variable, or a function or expression that can be converted to a positive, whole (integer) number.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aep1665702782656__p_d82844e1_d82845e1_d82846e1\">The result of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fact</span> must be less\n            than 1 * 10 <sup class=\"ph sup\">9999</sup> , which means that <var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var> must be positive and\n            less than 3249.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aep1665702782656__topic_d54692e1_d54693e1_d54694e1_d54695e1_d54696e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d966743e99\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aep1665702782656__p_d82850e1_d82851e1_d82852e1\">Calculated factorial of <var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aep1665702782656__p_d82853e1_d82854e1_d82855e1\">If an error occurs, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"aep1665702782656__table_d8459e1_d8460e1_d8461e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fact</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"aep1665702782656__table_d8459e1_d8460e1_d8461e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value \n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"aep1665702782656__table_d8459e1_d8460e1_d8461e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"aep1665702782656__table_d8459e1_d8460e1_d8461e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aep1665702782656__table_d8459e1_d8460e1_d8461e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n -1204\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aep1665702782656__table_d8459e1_d8460e1_d8461e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n &lt;UPROCERR_NEGATIVE&gt;\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aep1665702782656__table_d8459e1_d8460e1_d8461e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Negative value not allowed.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aep1665702782656__table_d8459e1_d8460e1_d8461e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n -1206\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aep1665702782656__table_d8459e1_d8460e1_d8461e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n &lt;UPROCERR_INTEGER&gt;\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aep1665702782656__table_d8459e1_d8460e1_d8461e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Not an integer.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aep1665702782656__table_d8459e1_d8460e1_d8461e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n -1208\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aep1665702782656__table_d8459e1_d8460e1_d8461e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n &lt;UPROCERR_OVERFLOW&gt;\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aep1665702782656__table_d8459e1_d8460e1_d8461e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Overflow.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aep1665702782656__topic_d54697e1_d54698e1_d54699e1_d54700e1_d54701e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d966743e192\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aep1665702782656__p_d82859e1_d82860e1_d82861e1\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aep1665702782656__section_svv_kly_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d966743e202\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fact</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example returns the factorial of 13:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"aep1665702782656__pre_nz2_lly_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vFactorial = $fact(13)\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525649\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525649\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$fact Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $fact Calculate the factorial of X (X!). $fact ( X ) Parameters X —positive integer constant, or a field (or indirect reference to a field), a variable, or a function or expression that can be converted to a positive, whole (integer) number. The result of $fact must be less than 1 * 10 9999 , which means that X must be positive and less than 3249. Return Values Calculated factorial of X . If an error occurs, $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 1. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $fact Value Error constant Meaning -1204 <UPROCERR_NEGATIVE> Negative value not allowed. -1206 <UPROCERR_INTEGER> Not an integer. -1208 <UPROCERR_OVERFLOW> Overflow. Use Allowed in all component types. Example: Using $fact The following example returns the factorial of 13: vFactorial = $fact(13) Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}